The charges match Carrie's diary.

263
00:16:33,676 --> 00:16:34,977
She could have followed him.

264
00:16:35,068 --> 00:16:36,763
Sweetie, it's very specific.

265
00:16:38,851 --> 00:16:40,654
And I don't want you seeing Kid Rock.

266
00:16:48,408 --> 00:16:49,501
Dr. Levine's office.

267
